==Preferences==

The default diffuse color and transparency of [[PartDesign_CompDatums|PartDesign datums]] is controlled by the {{MenuCommand|DefaultDatumColor}} [[Fine-tuning#PartDesign_Workbench|fine-tuning parameter]].

